{
  "texts": [
    "BBN: Provides a fine-grained entity annotation reference.",
    "WikiGold: Using Wikipedia's large, semi-structured features to create NER datasets.",
    "FSU-PRGE/PRO-GENE: The goal of the PROGENE is to create a large, comprehensive and reliably annotated protein/gene corpus that can be used for supervised training and quality assessment based on machine learning in the domain of biology [27].",
    "WiNER: Training the NER system by continuously creating NER datasets based on encyclopedic texts to improve the performance of the system.",
    "OntoNotes 5.0: The goal of the OntoNotes project is to create a research resource that is applicable in many aspects of the field of natural language processing by annotating a large corpus."
  ]
